brief_summary.textblock:
This prospective study is focused on the validation of the genetic signature of 27 genes as a
predictor of the response to concomitant chemotherapy treatment followed by brachytherapy in
patients with locally advanced cervical cancer. The genes included are: ZNF238; SAP30;
C10orf137; UHRF1; SUZ12; HMGN4; RBBP4; PPP1CB; SLFN11; FLJ39378; ENDOGL1; RECQL; TRPC1; TRIO;
DNAH6; GNL3L; SLC36A2; SRP9; RPE; LDOC1L; PUS7L; CCDC89; LOC644921; PLEKHG1; FAM111B; RPRD2 y
ETAA16.
